Package edu.ncsu.csc216.issue_manager.model.manager

Class IssueList

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.issue_manager.model.manager.IssueList
  • public class IssueList
extends java.lang.Object
    A IssueList maintains a List of Issues and supports the addition of a list, a collection of issues, removing an issue, searching for an issue and return the entire list or sublists of the list by type.
    Author:
    Sanjana Cheerla
